==English==
===Noun===
'''Catalyst'''
#{{chemistry}} A [[substance]], used in relatively small amounts, which increases the [[rate]] of a [[chemical]] [[reaction]] without being consumed in the process.
#(''automobile'') A [[catalytic converter]].
#one who helps or [[encourage]]s [[progress]] or [[change]]
#:''I hope the new CEO will be a [[catalyst]] for change.''

